Name: Dog Cat Pet Hair Dryer Grooming Blow Speed Hairdryer Blower Heater Blaster 2800W
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Dogs love to jump and play in everything. You have washed your dog yet again from their mud bath! At least this time you can dry them off quickly. A happy dog is a dry and clean dog.

No more wet dog smell around the house. Clean your fluffy dog then dry them straight away with your new dog hair dryer. Faster drying means a healthier dog particularly for long-haired breeds.

It is almost cross between a vacuum cleaner and a blow dryer. Just select the right setting and point the nozzle at your pet’s fur. Keep moving the nozzle over your pet until they are dried. Easy.

Your dog will soon learn to love their pet blow dryer. Introduce it to them slowly and start at a lower temperature and speed. Get them used to it over a few sessions. Start slow but dry fast.

We are not saying this is perfect to dry children with. We would never say that. If you happened to have a wet child and wanted them dry fast. Well this pet hair dryer does a great job of drying.

Key Features:

  • Thermal control
  • Airflow control
  • Quick and safe drying
  • Low noiseoperation
  • Three different nozzles
  • Insulated handle
  • Flexible hose
  • Easy to use

Name: Dog Cat Water Bottle for Drinking Walking Portable Travel GREY
Description:
Dog Cat Water Bottle for Drinking Walking Portable Travel

EASY TO USE ONE HANDED OPERATION

- Dog water bottle is designed to be easily used with just one hand. Use one thumb to dispense the water with one button, feed your dog, retract the remaining water and lock the bottle. All this whilst letting you keep a hold of your dog's leash with your other hand

LEAK PROOF DESIGN

- You want to know when you carry your pet water bottle for walking, hiking or camping, that it won't leak. This dog travel accessory has a silicon leak proof seal and a lock button to prevent any spills

PORTABLE & LIGHTWEIGHT

- Light dog travel accessories are important, so our small capacity size bottle weighs only 135 grams and our big pet water bottle only 160g (without water). We made it this way so you don't think twice before taking your bottle with you to the beach, walking, hiking or travelling on any adventure

LARGE & SMALL OPTIONS

- We love that dogs come in all sizes and so should our pet travel accessories. With 350ml and 550ml sizes you can cater for just one small puppy all the way up to multiple large dogs. Bottle attachments are interchangeable between cups / troughs

HEALTHY ALTERNATIVE TO PUBLIC WATER BOWLS

- Nothing worries a dog owner more than wondering whether your puppy or dog should drink from a public bowl but we want to keep our furry friends well hydrated, especially in the hot Australian climate.

Name: Grass Potty Dog Pad Training Pet Puppy Indoor Toilet Artificial Trainer Portable
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Help solve where your dog goes to toilet. Use the dog potty either as a training tool or a permanent solution. Very handy for those in apartments or those without backyards. Save your floor and wallet at the same time.

The resilient and non-toxic construction will last you a long time and keep you puppy or dog safe. Pick between two convenient sizes based on how large your dog is. The larger version has an artificial wall that will mean even larger dogs will not leave a mess everywhere.

Save on cost and help the environment by reducing the need for using puppy pads or newspaper. Purchase once, use for a long time without the need to replace parts every day. The removable container can be easily cleaned and requires no special cleaning products.

With a three-layer system, clean-up and maintenance will be a breeze. If the grass gets damaged, there are replacement mats available. Each potty comes with two grass mats so you can use one whilst the other is being cleaned.

Key Features:

  • Three-layer system
  • Odourless and non-toxic
  • Good drainage
  • Anti-microbial construction
  • Premiumsynthetic grass mat
  • Removable waster drawer
  • Well-suited forpotty training
  • Easy clean-up
SPECIFICATION

Brand: PaWz

Material: PE and PP

Colour: Green and black

Grass mat L: 72cm x  46cm

Grid tray: 76cm x 51cm
